Author: tradershub
Title: ‚≠ê [ANN][ICO] Tradershub - Ultimate Gateway Into the Crypto World ‚≠ê
Body: Dear Tradershub supporters!  It's hard to tell bad news, but unfortunately the situation is inevitable. Despite our community‚Äôs generous contributions, we did not manage to reach our softcap target. We‚Äôd be lying if we said we are not disappointed. We have invested a lot of effort, time and money in the project and gave up many things along the way. Unfortunately, it was not enough. All invested ETH are safe and will be refunded to our contributors in the upcoming days. Consequently the THT token has self destruct, so no actual THT tokens will exist anymore. We will post details regarding refunds shortly.  We would like to thank each and every one of you for all the support you showed us in the past weeks. You are the reason that we will continue our efforts to reach our goals. We kindly ask you for understanding and are forever grateful for your contributions.  All the best, Tradershub Team

Author: tradershub
Title: ‚≠ê [ANN][ICO] Tradershub - Ultimate Gateway Into the Crypto World ‚≠ê
Body: https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/Tradershub_logo.png   Ultimate Gateway Into the Crypto World   Tradershub is a social trading platform that allows anyone to participate in the crypto economy.  By blending sophisticated engineering with an elegant user experience and crowd-sourced intelligence, we empower traders with everything they need to trade effectively within a trustworthy and safe trading environment.  Tradershub creates value by removing all friction points, encouraging cooperation amongst peers and incentivizing users to perform value-adding services for the benefit of the community as a whole.    https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/video_link.png  https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/telegram_link.png  https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/wp_link.png      Why Use Tradershub?  Tradershub aspires to address all major shortcomings within the crypto-trading technology and deliver a simpler, more intuitive solution for investors and traders, regardless of their experience level. With security as a priority, Tradershub is designed to amplify and streamline your analytic and execution performance while leveraging the power of a thriving community. Say goodbye to nerve-racking trading experience. With Tradershub you will be able to focus on making the best decisions possible and nothing else.    https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/devices.png   ICO Details  Token_Symbol THT Token_Standard ERC20 Softcap 3000 ETH Hardcap 12000 ETH Presale_Start_Date February 22, 2018 Presale_End_Date March 2, 2018 Presale_End_Date March 2, 2018 Crowdsale_Start_Date March 5, 2018 Crowdsale_End_Date March 26, 2018 Maximum_Total_THT_Issued 83,385,000   https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/charts.png    THT will be Tradershub‚Äôs principal payment unit, essentially functioning as an utility token. It will be used on the platform to pay fees, access various features, incentivize community building and content creation through a dynamic rewarding system.   https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/circulation.png      Join Our Growing Community  Development of Tradershub promises to be an amazing journey. All those interested in crypto trading are encouraged to join us.   https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/facebook.png https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/twitter.png https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/linkedin.png https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/youtube.png https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/instagram.png https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/medium.png https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/telegram.png https://storage.googleapis.com/tradershub-images/github.png    For more information vistit: Tradershub.io
